102
00:04:46,121 --> 00:04:48,851
- I just want you to be my witness.
- You want me to...

103
00:04:50,558 --> 00:04:52,287
be your best man?

104
00:04:52,394 --> 00:04:55,022
It's just a signature
I need on the license.

105
00:04:55,130 --> 00:04:57,462
My son's not old enough.
It's... It's no big deal.

106
00:04:57,565 --> 00:04:59,999
I will not take
this sacred duty lightly.

107
00:05:00,101 --> 00:05:05,505
I am gonna get you the single healthiest
call girl that this town has ever seen.

108
00:05:05,607 --> 00:05:07,808
