Tweedledee, Tweedledum.

113
00:05:19,354 --> 00:05:21,345
<i>Michael didn't mean it in that way.</i>

114
00:05:21,456 --> 00:05:23,981
<i>How could he?
He didn't even know.</i>

115
00:05:24,092 --> 00:05:27,152
