197
00:09:36,377 --> 00:09:38,845
<i>And Michael was waiting at the hotel.</i>

198
00:09:38,947 --> 00:09:41,211
Hey, Dad. Just wanted
to let you know...

199
00:09:41,316 --> 00:09:44,046
