I'm under house arrest.

207
00:10:05,073 --> 00:10:07,098
Let's watch something together.

208
00:10:08,910 --> 00:10:11,435
Wow. That Blossom grew up, huh?

209
00:10:11,546 --> 00:10:13,514
<i>Say, how's that shower comin'?</i>

210
00:10:13,615 --> 00:10:15,776
- All right, look, she's not in the shower.
