meet me at the hotel.

212
00:10:17,885 --> 00:10:21,377
I called you a little prematurely,
but she is coming. - Really?

213
00:10:25,993 --> 00:10:28,986
Uh! Hey, put Rita on.

214
00:10:29,097 --> 00:10:31,122
<i>That's when Michael finally accepted...</i>

215
00:10:31,232 --> 00:10:34,167
<i>that Rita wasn't coming...</i>

216
00:10:34,268 --> 00:10:37,362
