220
00:10:49,452 --> 00:10:52,250
<i>- Who is it?
- It's Michael, Rita. Can I come in?</i>

221
00:10:52,355 --> 00:10:55,324
<i>- I can't let you in.
- You didn't show up last night.</i>

222
00:10:55,425 --> 00:10:57,893
